FBIS3-8520 "dreeu048_i_94013" FBIS-EEU-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Serbs Mobilizing Underage Muslims, Croats AU1003202494 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 1800 GMT 10 Mar 94 AU1003202494 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Article by Smajl Terzic] [Excerpts] The fierce chetnik offensive activities in the operational zone of the 7th South Operative Group did not stop today. The aggressor has been pounding (?Pjeskovita Kosa) and (?Bejici) with artillery and launching infantry attacks and has refused to halt his efforts to take control of the Doboj-Teslic road; however, all has been in vain. [passage omitted] The chetniks continue to mobilize Muslims and Croats, even those under age, in Doboj and Teslic and to send them to the front lines.
